flowchart TD
    Source[File / Web / Repo / Note] --> Register[Register Source]
    Register --> Privacy[Classify Privacy Tier]
    Privacy --> Parse[Parse: Unstructured / Crawl4AI]
    Parse --> Clean[Clean & Normalize]
    Clean --> Chunk[Chunk with Metadata]
    Chunk --> Embed[Generate Embeddings]
    Embed --> Qdrant[Qdrant Vector Index]
    Chunk --> DB[Canonical DB Chunks]
    Qdrant --> Eval[Ingestion Quality Eval]
    DB --> Eval
    Eval --> Ready[Ready for Retrieval]
    Ready --> Reflection[Reflection Job - flags stale sources, ADR 0010]
